====Verb====
{{en-verb|mir|ing}}

# To weigh down.

===Etymology 2===
Perhaps related to Middle Dutch [[miere]] (Dutch [[mier]]).

====Noun====
{{en-noun-reg}}

# ''(obsolete):'' An [[ant]].

